product.title: Galaxy Moon Heart Gold-Plated Asymmetric Stud Earrings
product.body_html:
The perfect blend of celestial elegance and heartfelt charm

A symbol of love and companionship to take with you wherever you go, this galaxy-themed heart stud earring is made from copper and 18K real gold plating. With a light pink/purple stone at the center and small details, this is the piece to add to your earring stack.

Crafted with meticulous attention to detail and available in three stunning finishes - Gold, Silver, and Rose Gold - these earrings are designed to add a touch of magic to your everyday style.

  • Shape: Heart
  • Metal Type: Copper
  • Material: 18K Real Gold-Plating
  • Category: Earrings (Stud)
  • Package includes: 1 Pair of Earrings
  • Packaging: Earrings do not come with the original box to protect the environment but they do come in a plastic bag. Let's save our planet together from unnecessary waste.
  • Maintenance: 18k gold-plated jewelry will not fade. If the color becomes darker, wash it with soap to restore the brightness.

 
But what truly sets these earrings apart is their unique asymmetry. One earring is longer and showcases the heart and moon with twinkly stars, while the other is shorter and gleams with a blue dangling gem, making both your ears stand out with a touch of cosmic wonder.

A wonderful gift for your loved ones

Whether you're looking for a thoughtful gift for your partner, a sweet surprise for your sister, or a token of love for your mom, these Galaxy-themed Heart Stud Earrings are the perfect choice. Representing love, dreams, and the limitless beauty of the night sky, making them a meaningful present for any occasion.

Elevate your jewelry collection today!
